game_description: Gods of Gravity is a social, arcade-style RTS game where you compete in an epic showdown of celestial gods. Scoop up ships and fling them to capture a nearby planet, or open wormholes to teleport them across the solar system. Hold planets and moons to boost your production. Mine asteroids for the powerful resources within. And if you dare, capture the sun for the ultimate buff. Then send a massive fleet to conquer your enemy’s home planet. Last god standing wins. 2 to 8 Player Multiplayer: ● Eliminate your opponents to take control of the solar system ● Command your own fleet or team up with friends against bots ● Socialize with built-in, spatial voice chat Single Player Campaign: ● Take over the galaxy, one solar system at a time ● Unlock new Gods with game-changing powers Ranked: ● Fight your way to the top of the ranked leaderboard ● Compete in livestreamed tournaments Challenges: ● Earn cosmetic rewards ● Personalize your God with titles, crowns, trails, and more
review_2: Gods of gravity should be game of the century. Gods of gravity is a fast-paced game where you send ships/troops to planets and capture them to win the game. It even has cosmetics. You should definitely play gods of gravity. (Edit) please make more maps free or ultra cheaper I feel like I can't do anything because I don't have ultra
review_3: To put it blunt. The game itself is amazing for those of you who love fast-paced strategy games. This is definitely the game for you. The community itself it amazing with amazing people who are willing to teach you how to play the game if need be It's strongly recommended to get this for sure.
review_4: Gods of Gravity is one of, if not the, best RTS games on the quest line up. Featuring 1-1 to 5vffa and even co-op or competitive modes this free game can be that “play with the boys” or “go for gold” experience you been looking for. Graphics are simple yet stylized. Gameplay is in the sweet-spot of “easy to learn, hard to master”. The community is generally good as long as you avoid the squeakers. All around a great experience you should play at least once, and hopefully stay for more. (If you see me in game after reading this say “Silly Nathan” to me with no context)
review_5: THIS IS AN AMAZING STRATEGY GAME!! i 100% recommend it, i’ve been following this game ever since September 2022-ish!! pleasee download this it has very good graphics and the game is generally really fun to play. not a big fan of the new god avatars, but i will continue to support this game because the game is just too fun to stop playing! (to be fair, i mainly play vrchat and GoG but thats besides the point) TL;DR, definitely buy this game. amazing for free to play players.
